name: Side Effects
description:
This piece of art is the collaboration of Size Music TH x Bright Me To The Moon

This is my first motion collage artwork which is inspired from side effects of my pills. I tried happily and excitedly to describe and put my feeling at that moment and side effects into this piece. 

My additional story of this artwork will be posted on my Twitter, that is linked on this H=N account, after be minted this work a few days.

Hope you love this!
Have a great time!

love,
